article.description: — Darin Green Jr. had 11 points as Central Florida defeated Jacksonville 63-54 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Green Jr. scores 11 to lift UCF over Jacksonville 63-54
article.linkText: Green Jr. scores 11 to lift UCF over Jacksonville 63-54
article.story: ORLANDO, Fla. -- — Darin Green Jr. had 11 points as Central Florida defeated Jacksonville 63-54 on Tuesday night. Dre Fuller Jr. had six rebounds for Central Florida (3-0). Darius Perry added six assists. Tommy Bruner had 13 points for the Dolphins (2-1). Jordan Davis added 13 points.
